_:b0__80932 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((4.75 69.15,22.14 69.15,22.14 55.23,4.75 55.23,4.75 69.15))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
