}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#c574e053a6c9b0ce4d6c5244d21bc1b1>.
<#c574e053a6c9b0ce4d6c5244d21bc1b1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d7568ec4-d9e0-4f8f-bf01-e9f672a79198>;
