    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021003153>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Bibliographical details of all first editions of novels translated into Swedish between 2000–2015 (except for novels from the Harlequin publishing company).  There are two datafiles: the larger reference database of 5259 direct AND indirect translations and the database consisting only of the 70 indirect translations published in Swedish in Sweden between 2000–2015.\nEndNote is recommended to read the RIS-file, but Zotero should also work."@en, "Det är två filer i datasetet. Den större består av bibliografisk data för de 5259 (direkt OCH indirekt) översatta romaner som publicerats p�� svenska i Sverige år 2000-2015. Den mindre filen består av bibliografisk data om de 70 indirekt översatta romaner som publicerats på svenska i Sverige 2000-2015.\nFilerna läses enklast i EndNote men borde gå att läsa även i Zotero eller andra referenshanteringssystem."@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/970b-bd59#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-07-29T12:36:28.384986Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.5878/970b-bd59>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2025-07-29T12:36:28.384986Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Bibliographical data concerning the 5259 first editions of novels translated into Swedish 2000-2015"@en, "Bibliografiska data om de 5259 romaner översatta till svenska som publicerats i förstautgåva i Sverige åren 2000-2015"@sv;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/EDUC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__81323.
_:b0__81323 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2015-12-31"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#startDate> "2000-01-01"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/PeriodOfTime>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/970b-bd59> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>
