<#e2129f88ddd859ad44013f417823f91c> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://ckan-malmo.dataplatform.se/dataset/75659637-4798-4aec-83d7-588fd5301ecb/resource/b1e2f2d3-6cea-4759-8e42-5ca399735f27>;
